[resource]
script = ExtResource("1_a4a53")
title = "Ruboleum Distillation Instructions"
text = "Trial #13: First Successful Inhibitor

Distill Ruboleum by pouring a vial into an opaque flask. Heat the flask with an open flame and wait for the substance to vaporize. When the vapor returns to a purified liquid form and drains into the cup, it should be potent enough to temporarily remedy the delirium caused by Vitriscet.

The substance is fast acting, though the amount of time it remains effective is rather short, only a few minutes. Vorrumos willing, this may save us.

Each consecutive dose prolongs the relief, but only to an extent. Any doses taken after the third consecutive dose appear to have no benefit. As such, those afflicted can take up to three doses at a time for maximum effectiveness.

The ruboleum burns clean; no residue, no waste. Brother Aldric says it's magic. I think it's just good alchemy."
important = true
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://c47e3n15issfv"
